
main.edc: build time options

This options disables or enables mouse pointer pulsating animation
	#define USE_ANIMATED_CURSOR (0/1)

Set this option to 1 to lower ibar icons opacity
	#define FADE_BAR_ICONS (0/1)

This options enables or disables the view of context menu title
	#define SEE_CONTEXT_MENUTITLE (0/1)

COMPILING and INSTALLING:

To compile and install:
	make

To uninstall:
	make uninstall

